    <item>
      <title>苏纳克谴责香港对言论自由“冠军”的审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/sunak-condemns-hong-kong-s-trial-of-free-speech-champion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相苏纳克谴责香港对黎智英的审判是“出于政治动机”，这使他成为迄今为止唯一一位参与听证会的世界领导人，这位前媒体大亨可能被判处终身监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/sunak-condemns-hong-kong-s-trial-of-free-speech-champion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 10:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
