    <item>
      <title>汗的政党将“蝙蝠”作为巴基斯坦民意调查的象征，这是重大缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/khan-s-party-gets-bat-as-pakistan-poll-symbol-in-major-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦法院允许前总理伊姆兰·汗所在的政党以板球棒为标志参加下个月的全国选举，这对于这位试图让政党重新掌权的前板球运动员、政治家来说是一个重大的缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/khan-s-party-gets-bat-as-pakistan-poll-symbol-in-major-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>假新闻危险成为选举年达沃斯的首要担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/fake-news-danger-becomes-top-davos-worry-in-year-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界经济论坛的一项调查显示，在选举和经济苦差事交织在一起的情况下，虚假或错误信息将成为未来两年世界面临的最大危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/fake-news-danger-becomes-top-davos-worry-in-year-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平提升中国与创纪录国家的关系以对抗美国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/xi-elevates-ties-with-record-number-of-nations-to-counter-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平去年与创纪录数量的国家升级了外交关系，寻求团结全球南方，帮助重塑美国领导的世界秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/xi-elevates-ties-with-record-number-of-nations-to-counter-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国高级特使表示，北京在台湾问题上没有妥协的余地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/china-envoy-says-beijing-has-no-room-to-compromise-on-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国和中国之间的关系更广泛地显示出稳定的迹象，但在周六台湾总统选举之前，北京和台北之间的言论正在升温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/china-envoy-says-beijing-has-no-room-to-compromise-on-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 19:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国采取行动禁止娱乐性使用大麻，阻碍新兴产业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/thailand-moves-to-end-recreational-cannabis-use-in-setback-for-nascent-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国提出了一项新立法，禁止除医疗和健康相关目的外使用大麻——自该国成为亚洲第一个将植物合法化以来，为控制娱乐消费而做出的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/thailand-moves-to-end-recreational-cannabis-use-in-setback-for-nascent-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:49:50 GMT</pubDate>
